{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/join_discord.png?t=1732883408\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>The Lightkeeper Is Gone</i> is a retro-stylized slow-burn horror adventure centered around a lighthouse keeper's mysterious disappearance</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Working on a lighthouse far away from civilization is a demanding job that takes a resilient spirit and iron discipline. The L\u2014\u2014 Isle has only seen two keepers to date\u2014and while the first managed well enough, the recent hire has turned out to be more of a nuisance. Their departure has left the light dark; someone must take their place. Will you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/arriving.gif?t=1732883408\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover the previous keeper's story piece by piece</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're given an explanation, but it seems underwhelming. Seek out clues, but be careful\u2014not everything is as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/dialogue.gif?t=1732883408\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Look after the lighthouse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You've taken on a grave responsibility, and failing your duties will have consequences. The light must be started every evening\u2014and make sure the lens stays clean!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/work.gif?t=1732883408\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Take in the atmosphere</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Such a life is not for everyone, but you don't need anyone except for yourself. You will be given a lot of time to reflect upon your actions here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/crate.gif?t=1732883408\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Game's Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> several hours long choice-driven story told through the eyes of a new lighthouse keeper; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> multiple endings influenced by your actions; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> free exploration to uncover hidden details; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> engaging lighthouse maintenance mechanics inspired by real-world practices; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> an immersive, atmospheric world; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> a fishing mechanic.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3190760?t=1732883408","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3190760?t=1732883408","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/4bc60c4f5f0ec7758abf274648c2fa3264f711b6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732883408","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/4bc60c4f5f0ec7758abf274648c2fa3264f711b6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732883408","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3296120,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190760/extras/join_discord.png?t=1732883408\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>The Lightkeeper Is Gone</i> is a retro-stylized slow-burn horror adventure centered around a lighthouse keeper's mysterious disappeara